CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 15, 1941, page 3 reads: " Mr. and Mrs. Jordan of 384 Return street, Aliquippa, announced the engagement of their daughter, Miss Johnnye Jordan (above)  to Edwin Owens, son of Mrs. Sarah Owens and the late Dr. G. W. Owens of Atlanta , GA, the wedding date has been set for Christmas day. -- Harris photo.
TitMainTitle: Portrait of Johnnye Jordan wearing two toned dress, braided necklace, and holding light colored cloth, posed seated on bench next to eyeglasses, in front of light colored circular patterned background, in Harris Studio
